#

Gourmet Grilled Veggie Sandwich

$8.5
450 kcal

Allergens:

Gluten

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianVeganHigh Fiber

Tags:

SandwichGrilledVegetarianHealthy

Description

A delicious grilled sandwich packed with vibrant vegetables and a zesty spread, perfect for a healthy meal.

Ingredients

  • Whole Grain Bread: 2 slices
  • Zucchini: 1 small, sliced
  • Red Bell Pepper: 1, sliced
  • Portobello Mushroom: 1, sliced
  • Avocado: 1/2, mashed
  • Spinach: 1 cup, fresh
  • Olive Oil: 1 tablespoon
  • Balsamic Vinegar: 1 teaspoon
  • Garlic Powder: 1/2 teaspoon
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
